#### Issue details
_If SpriteCache.draw() is called between SpriteCache.beginCache() and SpriteCache.endCache(), app crashes with fatal error._

#### Reproduction code
```
import ...;

public class Game extends ApplicationAdapter {
    SpriteCache spriteCache;
    Texture img;

    @Override
    public void create () {
        spriteCache = new SpriteCache();
        img = new Texture("badlogic.jpg");
    }

    @Override
    public void render () {
        Gdx.gl.glClearColor(1, 0, 0, 1);
        Gdx.gl.glClear(GL20.GL_COLOR_BUFFER_BIT);

        // Begin sprite cache drawing
        spriteCache.begin();

        // Prepare cache
        spriteCache.beginCache();
        spriteCache.add(img, 0f, 0f);
        int cacheIndex = spriteCache.endCache();

        // Draw cache
        spriteCache.draw(cacheIndex); // <- fatal error
        spriteCache.end();
    }
}
```

